Crispy Vietnamese Pancake (Banh Xeo)

Banh Xeo / Crispy Vietnamese Pancake is a Vietnamese sizzling pancake with prawns, bean shoots, and a flavoursome fish sauce, packed full of flavour with each bite. Try this recipe now! Brought to you by Asian Inspirations.
